        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\ceph\configuration_files.dita" xtrc="li:15;367:13">
          <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\ceph\configuration_files.dita" xtrc="codeph:6;368:19">sda</codeph>, <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\cinder\ceph\configuration_files.dita" xtrc="codeph:7;368:41">sdb</codeph> are used as system disks</li>
